8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-a:text-primary hover:prose-a:text-primary/80 prose-p:leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"lead text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-8","children":"At WA-AB, we believe that your data is your property. This Privacy Policy details the strict boundaries regarding how information is handled when using our open-source, self-hosted WhatsApp Gateway."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-2 mt-8 text-2xl border-b pb-2","children":[["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-lock h-6 w-6 text-blue-500","aria-hidden":"true","children":[["$","rect","1w4ew1",{"width":"18","height":"11","x":"3","y":"11","rx":"2","ry":"2"}],["$","path","fwvmzm",{"d":"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"}],"$undefined"]}],"1. Zero-Tracking Architecture"]}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Because WA-AB is designed to be ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"self-hosted"}],", all core data processing occurs exclusively on the hardware where you deploy the application."]}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"No Centralized Telemetry:"}]," The creators of WA-AB do not receive telemetry, analytics, or usage reports about your WhatsApp interactions."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Absolute Data Ownership:"}]," Your contacts, messages, schedules, and auto-replies remain in your own database. We cannot and will not access it."]}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"mt-8 text-2xl border-b pb-2","children":"2. Data We Process Locally"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When you deploy the gateway, the application running on your server interacts with:"}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Authentication Credentials:"}]," Passwords you create for the dashboard are securely hashed using bcrypt before being stored in your local database."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"WhatsApp Sessions:"}]," WA-AB acts as a bridge to WhatsApp Web. The session tokens (keys) necessary to maintain this connection are stored locally on your server."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Communication Logs:"}]," Messages sent and received via the gateway are logged within your local database to provide you with historical data and webhook functionality."]}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"mt-8 text-2xl border-b pb-2","children":"3. Protecting Your Information"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"While WA-AB is built with modern security practices, the ultimate safety of your data depends on your hosting environment. We strongly recommend:"}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":["Deploying the application behind a reverse proxy with enforced ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"SSL/TLS encryption"}]," (HTTPS)."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Securing the host server with firewalls and SSH key authentication."}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Keeping the underlying operating system and Node.js environment constantly updated."}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"mt-8 text-2xl border-b pb-2","children":"4. Third-Party Integrations"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["WA-AB utilizes the ",["$","code",null,{"children":"@whiskeysockets/baileys"}]," library to communicate directly with WhatsApp's servers. By using this gateway, your server will establish a direct web-socket connection to WhatsApp. Please be aware that your use of WhatsApp is still subject to Meta's Privacy Policy."]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12 p-6 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-2xl border border-blue-500/10","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"font-semibold mb-2","children":"Need Further Details?"}]